    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You gather Chakra in a specific part of your body (like a fist or foot) and attack with the body part, pushing out the Chakra at the same time.<br><br>Make an unarmed attack against the target, gaining a +1 damage bonus of the appropriate type.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 1 additional Chakra to increase the damage bonus by +1, up to +1 per level or +6 total. Increase the Perform Requirements by 1 for every 2 Chakra spent to empower the technique.</p>\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The fifth step grants an additional +1 damage to the attack, and increases the amount to which you can empower it by +1 as well.</p>\n",
